    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The constructor of the class InArray swallows its options. The options passed will not be submitted to the parent constructor.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
parent::__construct();
</code></pre>

<p>must be</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
parent::__construct($options);
</code></pre>

